text: Rosen Raychev (born 9 March 1967) is a Bulgarian equestrian. He competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Bulgaria Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:People from Dimitrovgrad, Bulgaria
